# Lime-Pickled Red Onions

---

## Ingredients

* 1 large red onion, thinly sliced
* 100 ml / 7 tbsp lime juice
* 1 tsp salt
* A few cracked peppercorns

## To serve

* Freshly chopped herbs, such as coriander (cilantro) or parsley
* 1 tsp sumac

---

## Steps

